<li> I am so sorry for your loss. May cherished memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li> Thinking of you and your family during this difficult time.</li>
<li> Words cannot express how saddened I am by your loss.</li>
<li> Sending my heartfelt condolences to you and your loved ones.</li>
<li> May the love and support of those around you help you through this.</li>
<li> Please accept my deepest condolences on the passing of your [relationship to deceased].</li>
<li> Your family is in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
