<li> May your memories of [deceased's name] bring you comfort and peace.</li>
<li> I’m so very sorry to hear of your loss. Please let me know if there is anything at all I can do.</li>
<li> Sending you strength and love as you navigate this difficult journey.</li>
<li> With deepest sympathy and heartfelt sorrow.</li>
<li> May peace find you in this time of sorrow.</li>
<li> I'm thinking of your family, sending you all my love and support.</li>
    

